{
  "texts": [
    "Influence of the dataset molecular diversityIn this section, we aim to investigate the influence of molecular diversity in the pretraining dataset on the quality of the learned representation.",
    "We investigated how the model performs when we add more scaffolds during training.",
    "We randomly selected five batches with 10,000 different scaffold families each.",
    "The model was trained with each set of 10,000 families separately.",
    "We then created incremental batches, starting with a batch size of 20,000 families and gradually increasing to 30,000, 40,000, and 50,000."
  ]
}